description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide a mixed use development in a building ranging from 1 to 12 storeys in height (plus basement) to provide a 1,652m Library (Use Class D1) a 108m Caf (Use Class A3), a 1,866m Primary Care Centre (Use Class D1) and 136 residential units with 43 basement parking spaces with access onto St Lukes Avenue and associated landscaping and servicing.
